{"id": "ChIJCyGWvfSAhYARVoUSujzOuqo", "rating": 4.2, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 718, "displayName": {"text": "FUSION DUMPLING", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Buzzy, no-frills eatery for Sichuan cuisine ranging from mild to hot in a narrow, red-hued setup.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJCyGWvfSAhYARVoUSujzOuqo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201MGFqTnNOM0puU0ZrellVVTFNblpuVm1JeGJXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The food was honestly amazing very authentic and rich in flavour, I’m honestly surprised at the low rating due to how good it was. The service was also impeccable. Very attentive and kind. The bathrooms was also VERY clean which a lot of restaurants in an America do not care for. So I really appreciated that too!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The food was honestly amazing very authentic and rich in flavour, I’m honestly surprised at the low rating due to how good it was. The service was also impeccable. Very attentive and kind. The bathrooms was also VERY clean which a lot of restaurants in an America do not care for. So I really appreciated that too!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "charlotte watkinson", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101589964862198468360/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeaZBT7-35jiJHoQ2n8HuFyweRy6dQC4XIq2PQKMfKTReeyiE0=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-17T21:09:12.472799143Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201MGFqTnNOM0puU0ZrellVVTFNblpuVm1JeGJXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201MGFqTnNOM0puU0ZrellVVTFNblpuVm1JeGJXYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580f4bd96210b:0xaabace3cba128556"}, {"name": "places/ChIJCyGWvfSAhYARVoUSujzOuqo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ob2FHUXRWRU50V0VJeVJteHJkWHB3YzBwVFIyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Nice decor, attentive staff, good selections of different dumplings, noodles and dishes. Interesting and fun presentation of food. The Dan Dan noodles and crispy Chileans sea bass are very good. Cold chili noodles in ice bowl was very creative, it is vegetarian and good flavor. Truffle dumplings is an interesting mix. Good selection of tea, we had the Puer tea was good. Overall a very good experience.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Nice decor, attentive staff, good selections of different dumplings, noodles and dishes. Interesting and fun presentation of food. The Dan Dan noodles and crispy Chileans sea bass are very good. Cold chili noodles in ice bowl was very creative, it is vegetarian and good flavor. Truffle dumplings is an interesting mix. Good selection of tea, we had the Puer tea was good. Overall a very good experience.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Angie L. Krackeler (Angie)", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101645572236820774446/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcZFMrS1bsn3CA4oZ7Gjk2ydEalVZTOjrx0Krzg_h7Mx6wQeFf=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-24T23:51:00.544205517Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ob2FHUXRWRU50V0VJeVJteHJkWHB3YzBwVFIyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ob2FHUXRWRU50V0VJeVJteHJkWHB3YzBwVFIyYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580f4bd96210b:0xaabace3cba128556"}, {"name": "places/ChIJCyGWvfSAhYARVoUSujzOuqo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oRWNrZGZlV3hJVlRkNmNFSkdSbmhGY1VkTVIzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "OMG I found this as a recommendation from ChatGPT for the best dumplings in San Francisco and it did not lie!! Soup dumplings were amazing!!! Also had their fried rice and that was also a bit.. probably the best I've had. If you're considering, the answer is yes! They are in demand tho so make a reservation if you can", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "OMG I found this as a recommendation from ChatGPT for the best dumplings in San Francisco and it did not lie!! Soup dumplings were amazing!!! Also had their fried rice and that was also a bit.. probably the best I've had. If you're considering, the answer is yes! They are in demand tho so make a reservation if you can", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kevin Williams", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111275187981924274860/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7qYAKkfIdREymk9YccFHuLodHnfL9hf9IwBUxQ5w84VbihUZMNQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-31T04:53:12.954086252Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oRWNrZGZlV3hJVlRkNmNFSkdSbmhGY1VkTVIzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oRWNrZGZlV3hJVlRkNmNFSkdSbmhGY1VkTVIzYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580f4bd96210b:0xaabace3cba128556"}, {"name": "places/ChIJCyGWvfSAhYARVoUSujzOuqo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poUlIzUlNVVEJRWlVsVVZWSlZSRXM1YjA1Qk5IYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Wow. Wow. WOW.\n\nThis place completely blew us away. We’ve had authentic Chinese food many times, and more often than not, it ends in disappointment… but not here. Every single dish was outstanding there truly wasn’t one miss. You can taste the elevated quality in every bite, from the freshness of the ingredients to the care put into the preparation. This is the kind of meal you keep thinking about long after you leave.\n\nFrom the outside, the restaurant looks small and unassuming, but once you step inside, it opens up into a beautiful, welcoming space. Seating is limited and there’s a sign-in sheet at the entrance, but trust me whatever the wait is, it’s worth it. Do not let that deter you.\n\nPricing was very reasonable for the quality and portion sizes, and the service was prompt and attentive throughout our visit. If I’m being extremely picky, the only minor hiccup was the room-temperature water at the table, which had a few floating particles, and we had to ask for ice more than once before it arrived. That said, this was such a small detail in an otherwise flawless experience.\n\nEverything was clean, beautifully prepared, and absolutely delicious. We left incredibly happy and can’t wait to come back. Highly recommend! This is a must-try. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Wow. Wow. WOW.\n\nThis place completely blew us away. We’ve had authentic Chinese food many times, and more often than not, it ends in disappointment… but not here. Every single dish was outstanding there truly wasn’t one miss. You can taste the elevated quality in every bite, from the freshness of the ingredients to the care put into the preparation. This is the kind of meal you keep thinking about long after you leave.\n\nFrom the outside, the restaurant looks small and unassuming, but once you step inside, it opens up into a beautiful, welcoming space. Seating is limited and there’s a sign-in sheet at the entrance, but trust me whatever the wait is, it’s worth it. Do not let that deter you.\n\nPricing was very reasonable for the quality and portion sizes, and the service was prompt and attentive throughout our visit. If I’m being extremely picky, the only minor hiccup was the room-temperature water at the table, which had a few floating particles, and we had to ask for ice more than once before it arrived. That said, this was such a small detail in an otherwise flawless experience.\n\nEverything was clean, beautifully prepared, and absolutely delicious. We left incredibly happy and can’t wait to come back. Highly recommend! This is a must-try. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ale Gonzalez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109104390805815988908/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_ETPgwDEjCOxlpQQYO5UiK_wOf1fxqGSXFjlowkJV5W9fFDqN9A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-03T02:19:02.745878806Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poUlIzUlNVVEJRWlVsVVZWSlZSRXM1YjA1Qk5IYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poUlIzUlNVVEJRWlVsVVZWSlZSRXM1YjA1Qk5IYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580f4bd96210b:0xaabace3cba128556"}, {"name": "places/ChIJCyGWvfSAhYARVoUSujzOuqo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xJMmNsZEVPSEoxY2pKaFpFdDJXbkJMVVRabllrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Some of the best dumplings I've ever had. The server was attentive and quick to pick up my mood. Cleared dishes quick, checked on me and made great recommendations. I'd go back,  and for the first time I left a 30% tip. We'll earned.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Some of the best dumplings I've ever had. The server was attentive and quick to pick up my mood. Cleared dishes quick, checked on me and made great recommendations. I'd go back,  and for the first time I left a 30% tip. We'll earned.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anthony Thomas", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117798427320496714987/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1_ztR2cBXv8PlSceprsCa1_mf3OLo0Lo-6QlifLMUqFHiwGFu=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-09-30T04:29:52.416525015Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xJMmNsZEVPSEoxY2p